      <arrangement id="aspace_d6fa10f071c892d30ec9344dc786fd44">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically by subject, name, or form of material.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_9e0484d3766a83417a5c13b695393bc3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Yale University celebrated its 275th anniversary on 15 October 1976. The records primarily consist of background materials, drafts and transcripts of ceremonial remarks, and writings by invited speakers, including a commemorative poem by Archibald Macleish.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
